        <section class="cases-ps">
            <div class="case-info1">
                <h5>People often disregard the health of their skin.</h5>
                <p class="c-info"><span style="text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:700;">Problem</span><br>Almost
                    everyone has a hectic lifestyle, maintaining a good work-life balance isn’t easy. Even finding the
                    time to do what we enjoy can be tough, more so for something as little as applying and re-applying
                    sunscreen — even though it’s crucially important for our health.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="case-info2">
                <h5>Use of incentives is the key.</h5>
                <p class="c-info"><span style="text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:700;">Solution</span><br>Provide a
                    platform that lets its user find highly rated sunscreen products, see its reviews
                    instantly, tips on how to use them correctly, and reminders that notify them to re-apply. To keep
                    users engaged in using the app, a points system should be implemented where they can earn points for
                    doing their daily application and exchange these points to donate to non-profit organizations.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>
